Completed many Gundabad: Reclaiming the Mountain-hold quests assisting in Reclaiming the Mountain-hold.
Your efforts have truly assisted those who work to reclaim the mountain-home of Gundabad. You will certainly be rewarded for your accomplishments.
Completed Gundabad: Reclaiming the Mountain-hold quests ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Zóva, advisor to Prince Ingór, has requested your aid in the continued efforts to reclaim Gundabad for all dwarves.

Gundabad: Reclaiming the Mountain-hold quests are available from Zádokh Flint-eye, Agátur the Boastful, and Bráthi at Zidir-nesad, The Steepset.\n\nYou should talk to these dwarves as soon as you are able.

'We must reclaim Gundabad for all dwarves!\n\n'I ask for your help to aid in this effort. If you are able to complete several tasks for Zádokh Flint-eye, Agátur the Boastful, and Bráthi, we will be able to reward your accomplishments.'
